        class="feature-list experience"
      >
      	<li class="item">
	       <details>
         	<summary>
           	<date>2022 - present</date>
          	<h3 class="h4"><span>Front End Developer </span> - Series Eight</h3>
          </summary>
	         <div>At Series Eight, I've worked with multiple CMS's - Shopify, CraftCMS and Webflow - providing award winning websites and user experiences. Most recently, I've been part of a specialised team to handle retained and ongoing clients - allowing for improved client relationships and improved processes.</div>
	       </details>
       </li>
