						<ul class="stacked">
							<li>Implementation of scalable systems.</li>
							<li>Modern feature sets including CSS Grid, Flexbox, and Custom Properties.</li>
							<li>Performant interaction design and complex web animations.</li>
							<li>Responsive, fluid typography and layout systems.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
       	</li>
